Quickstrike:




Quickstrike froze as he saw Dark Mouse approach him and just stand there, 
smiling. It made him feel odd, nervous even. He kept by Black Arachnia, 
still wanting to talk to her.

He frowned at Dark Mouse. "What are ya starin' at? Finally realize ya own 
me, huh?"
